channel.title: Ghey PSD...Help? :-\
channel.description:
Mmmk, so last night i was making a sig, and it was looking good, but i had to get off so i saved it as a psd. And now i can't open it, it says "Could not complete your request because the file is not compatible with this version of Photoshop". I can open other psd's, but not this one, it doesn't really matter because i got the stock from my pack, but i don't want it to happen if i do an awesome sig then i forget what i do if i want to make a tutorial.
So, thanks in advance. -Kaza.
